headline: Parker-Hannifin price target raised to $960 from $930 at Baird
summary: Baird analyst Mircea Dobre raised the firm’s price target on Parker-Hannifin (PH) to $960 from $930 and keeps an Outperform rating on the shares. The firm updated its model following the announcement of its filtration acquisition which Baird said they like.
